《'''春天的开花树'''》（Vasanthathile Poomarangal），是政治活动家[[普利文|普利文]]（他被描述为[[毛主义者|毛主义者]]）化名Roopesh写的小说，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kozhikode/Flowers-of-spring-that-failed-to-bloom-in-Karala/articleshow/22108784.cms|title=Flowers of spring that failed to bloom in Karala|publisher=Times of India|accessdate=27 June 2014|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101020651/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kozhikode/Flowers-of-spring-that-failed-to-bloom-in-Karala/articleshow/22108784.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[DC_Books|DC Books]]将该小说命名为《'''毛主义者'''》（Maoist），而[[Green_Books|Green Books]]的标题为《春天的开花树》（Vasanthathile Poomarangal）。<ref name=publishing>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailypioneer.com/nation/publishers-slug-it-out-over-absconding-maoists-novel.html|title=Publishers Slug It Out Over Absconding Maoists Novel|publisher=Daily Pioneer|accessdate=27 June 2014|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504142649/https://www.dailypioneer.com/nation/publishers-slug-it-out-over-absconding-maoists-novel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这部小说是根据对喀拉拉邦毛主义者的报道编写的。它讲述了政治人物的活动以及警察在此问题上的干预。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kochi/Cops-closing-in-on-Maoist-leader-Roopesh/articleshow/9791018.cms|publisher=Times of India|accessdate=27 June 2014|title=Cops closing in on Maoist leader Roopesh|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608220249/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kochi/Cops-closing-in-on-Maoist-leader-Roopesh/articleshow/9791018.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

